{{!
  PROFILE CUSTOM TABS SNIPPET

  Adds the "Inklings" tab to the character profile page tab list.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs

  IMPORTANT: This file might be empty or minimal if you don't have other custom profile tabs.

  STEP 1: Check the file contents
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs
  2. Look at what's in the file:
     - If it's EMPTY or has only comments, use "OPTION A" below
     - If it has existing <ul> with <li> entries, use "OPTION B" below

  If the file is empty, copy ONLY this:

  ---START COPY HERE---
  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab" href="#inklings-tab-pane">Inklings</a>
  </li>
  ---END COPY---

  IMPORTANT:
  - DO NOT change the href="#inklings-tab-pane" - it must match the
    id="inklings-tab-pane" in profile-custom.snippet.hbs
  - Complete Step 2 of the README (Install Web Portal Components) first,
    which includes copying inklings-tab.js and other web files.
    The web portal integration is entirely optional.
}}
